Dynasty Genius — Product Management plugin (dg-pm)

This plugin is a derivative work reframed from the "product-management" plugin
in Anthropic's knowledge-work-plugins repository
(https://github.com/anthropics/knowledge-work-plugins), which is licensed under
the Apache License, Version 2.0.

Modifications from the original (2026-07-10):
- Rescoped from a multi-user SaaS product-management workflow to Dynasty Genius,
  a single-user, local-first ML asset-management project.
- Replaced external SaaS connectors (Slack, Linear, Notion, Figma, Amplitude,
  Intercom, Fireflies) with DG's own repo artifacts (AGENT_SYNC, agent ledger,
  governance files, spec/plan dirs, memory, GitHub via gh, the Codex/Gemini
  cockpit). See SOURCES.md.
- Bound every skill to DG working law: the No-Verdict Line
  (decision_supported=false; no verdicts/directives/nominated targets in
  running-software output), cockpit-TDD (Claude spec -> Codex RED -> Claude
  GREEN -> dual-CLEAR [Claude + Codex binding; Gemini advisory/non-binding] ->
  David authorizes), and David-authorizes-every-action.
- Rewrote write-spec to emit a DG spec of record (falsification seeds / RED
  matrix, cockpit-TDD sequence) instead of a generic PRD.
- Reframed roadmap-update onto AGENT_SYNC + the David-sequenced priority board;
  stakeholder-update onto a single-audience David update / session closeout;
  metrics-review onto descriptive model/operational telemetry (never a verdict);
  synthesize-research onto DG's adversarial research-lane pattern.
- Dropped sprint-planning, product-brainstorming, competitive-brief, and the
  brainstorm command (brainstorming is served by the existing
  superpowers:brainstorming skill).

